headline: A Look At Snap On’s Valuation As Q4 Beat And Dividend Hike Extend Its Growth Story
summary: Why Snap-on’s latest earnings matter for investors Snap-on (SNA) just released fourth quarter and full year 2025 results, reporting slightly higher quarterly sales and earnings per share, and announcing a 14% dividend increase, its 16th straight year of raising payouts. See our latest analysis for Snap-on.
